    • Method Detail

      • answer

        public JsonPathQuestionPlugin.JsonPathAnswerElement answer()
        This procedure proceeds as follows:
        • Compute the inner answer
        • Then, for each path query, do computeResult which returns JsonPathResult
        • The result is a list of JsonPathResultEntry minus exception entries
        • It also contains the result of evaluating the assertion on the result
        Specified by:
        answer in class Answerer

      • answerDiff

        public AnswerElement answerDiff()
        Description copied from class: Answerer
        The default implementation for generating differential answers.

        It uses TableDiff if the answer element is a TableAnswerElement. Otherwise, it uses a JSON-level diff.

        Answerers that want a custom differential answer, should override this function.

        Overrides:
        answerDiff in class Answerer
